I Don't get why she was so convinced, that she couldn't give her baby a good life.. Kids don't have to have parents who make a ton of money, to be completely happyand taken care of properly..

Her ENTIRE FAMILY LOOKED VERY WELL TAKEN CARE OF AND SEEMS EDUCATED..

HER BABY WOULD HAVE DEFINITELY PUSHED HER.... TO RISE UP A THOUSAND TIMES AGAIN..

THAT WAS A BLACK (biracial) BABY.. MAYBE SHE DIDN'T THINK SHE COULDN'T HANDLE WHAT CAME WITH THAT🤷🏽‍♀️.

MY DAUGHTER HAD MY GRANDSON AT 18, WAS IN COLLEGE, TOOK MATERNITY LEAVE, BACK TO COLLEGE SHE WENT.. SHE GRADUATED AT 22 WITH HER REGISTERED NURSING DEGREE.. AT 26 SHE BOUGHT HER FIRST HOUSE... BUILT FROM THE DIRT UP.. ALL BY HERSELF AS A SINGLE PARENT, SHE HAS CONTINUED BEING IN COLLEGE, SINCE SHE GRADUATED TO GET HER NEXT DEGREE.. I REPEAT.. WHILE SHE'S A SINGLE PARENT, DOES HER 18 HRS SHIFTS, VOLUNTEERS ON HER OFF DAYS, IN COLLEGE.. MY GSON (8 YRS OLD) IS ON A HANDPICKED, ELITE FOOTBALL TEAM.. #2 OF THE TOP 2 TEAMS IN THE STATE... SHE MAKS SURE SHE SCHEDULES STUDY TIME AND PLAY DATES/ACTIVITIES WITH MY GRANDSON..

AT 3 YEARS OLD, SHE TOLD ME SHE, WANTED TO WORK AT THE HOSPITAL WITH SICK BABIES.. SHE NEVER WAVERED/CHANGED HER MIND... FROM 3 TO NOW 27..
SHE IS A LABOR AND DELIVERY, REGISTERED NURSE..

THE BOY AND HIS FAMILY WANTED HER TO HAVE AN ABORTION OR DO ADOPTION, AND BECAUSE SHE WOULDN'T HE BROKE UP WITH HER.. NOTHING AS STOPPED MY DAUGHTER'S *RISE UP....

I WISH THIS YOUNG LADY WOULD HAVE KEPT HER BABY.. SHE IS INTELLIGENT, CONSCIOUS, HAS A BIG HEART AND IS TALENTED.. SHE SHOULD HAD GIVEN HERSELF MORE CREDIT..
I KNOW SHE WOULD'VE BEEN A PHENOMENAL MOTHER AND PROVIDER FOR HER DAUGHTER..

I PERSONALLY COULD HAVE NEVER.... LET MY DAUGHTER HAVE AN ABORTION OR GIVE MY GSON UP.. I WOULD HAVE TAKEN HIM AND RAISED HIM.
THE END. PERIOD..
